Required Editions and User Permissions:
Available in: Lightning Experience
Available in: Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions
User Permission Needed: Enhanced Folder Sharing, Report Builder, Create and Customize Reports

To create a report that finds deals pushed out:
On the Analytics tab, select Create | Report, or on the Reports tab, click New Report.
Select Select Report Type | Opportunities | Opportunities with Historical Trending.
Enable Historical Trend Reporting for Opportunities in Setup.
For Show, select All Opportunities.
Filter for close dates later than they were in the past.
Click Run Report.
Compare the date in the Close Date — Historical column with the date in the Close Date — Today column.
title: Historical Trend Reporting in Salesforce
